title: Tony Blair Admits He Had No Idea How Many Migrants Would Come When EU Added Eastern Bloc
text: W ZEALAND - JULY 28: Former UK Prime Minister, Tony Blair, speaks during his five city Australasian speaking tour on July 28, 2011 in Auckland, New Zealand. In his only appearance in New Zealand, Blair will speak to audiences in Auckland before heading to Brisbane and Sydney to complete the tour tomorrow. (Photo by Images)
